From 027c209c0e19a393d6858b90a842bbba8846f771 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: PGSPC <agent@mlino.local>
Date: Sat, 11 Jul 2026 18:05:18 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] test(api): add unit tests for AuthService and
 OrganizationsService.assertMember
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Closes #3 (TASK-003).

- apps/api/src/auth/auth.service.spec.ts: register (happy path +
  duplicate email -> ConflictException), login (happy path + wrong
  password / non-existent email -> UnauthorizedException). Verifies
  the stored hash is never the plaintext password.
- apps/api/src/organizations/organizations.service.spec.ts:
  assertMember — existing member resolves, non-member -> Forbidden,
  non-existent org -> NotFound. organizations.service.ts itself is
  untouched (read-only per PGSPC.md's Files To Modify).
- apps/api/package.json: jest + ts-jest as devDependencies, "test"
  script, jest config block (apps/api had no test runner before this).
- .ai/PROJECT_STATE.md: note the test suite now exists, per this
  task's Definition of Done.

All tests use a mocked PrismaService — no real database connection,
per the acceptance criteria.

Verified:
- npm test --workspace=apps/api -> 9/9 passing
- npm run lint -> clean
- npm run build --workspace=apps/api -> 0 errors
